@node DameNumpy
@chapter DameNumpy
@cindex DameNumpy

Numpy is a library about algebra used as dependency in a lot of python
programs. We have classified the tests in basics, datatypes and
maths. Basics is related to the most common uses about the library
(sum vectors, transpose matrix, generate eye matrix, ...). Datatypes
